entries.s_4: Oh, hello. I'm Quharek. I help Shaneeka, our new chief engineer, maintain most of the electronics and machinery in Aurilia. Hopefully, Shaneeka will last longer that past chief engineers. They seem to get killed a lot.
entries.s_6: Tell me about the Nightsister headdress in the Adventurers' Guildhall.
entries.s_8: Isn't that the headdress from the Nightsister that Captain Sarguillo captured? I guess I shouldn't ask you that if you're asking me the same thing.
